{"tid":1553652,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[社會實驗] 如果屋企有藍底嘅家人其實都有解決辦法！","createTime":"2019-09-08T16:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T20:12:17.000Z","uid":171302,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a5910027a7e785b10b447493a228555fe5b3de","tid":1553652,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1261946/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1261946/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n參考返呢位巴打嘅post！小弟都做咗同樣嘅實驗！<br />\n短短兩個星期，已經見到有好大成效！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位巴打可以參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 上佢地睇開嘅YouTube block 晒所有藍絲嘅page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(超有用！本身屋企人有睇陳怡呢d仆街，而家轉睇晒視點31，城寨，吳志森)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 因為佢哋本身已經有蘋果動新聞，所以淨係需要set個notification 做always pop up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 安裝埋立場新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然就唔少得delete 左d藍/紅底app<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 入佢地wechat，unsubscribe所有紅底資訊，得返啲健康頻道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁就神不知鬼不覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.我知道大家鏟走唔到83台，但係可以set定時收看99台(例如每日6:30, 7:00 ,7:30, 8:00 及晚上黃金時段)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁就神不知鬼不覺就轉左台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然最好就安裝埋cable and now TV<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. Set 返個wifi 接去wifi repeater (好平,小米有得買, &lt;$100 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 咁就可以控制住佢哋條大動脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當佢哋唔聽話睇紅底野嗰陣，就熄左佢Wi-Fi<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6. Facebook 屋企人無，所以少一樣野煩！可以參考下以下方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>然後佢就比咗部電話我叫我幫佢搞<br />\n我開咗佢fb unlike哂所有藍絲同fake news page<br />\n再report同block埋<br />\n幫佢like咗立場，有線等等嘅page<br />\n跟手響佢fb將佢幾個成日分享fake news嘅朋友hide咗<br />\n再再幫佢比咗蘋果嗰三蚊同打開通知<br />\n<br />\n就係呢個時候我老豆見我咁熱心，<br />\n主動拎部電話比我話最近部電話好慢，<br />\n叫我睇吓咩事<br />\n作為孝子我當然會幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家研究緊部電視點刪樣Tvb新聞台<br />\n<br />\n做完之後我一個星期後就會驗收成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊參與呢個社會實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己父母自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c9305487d4aec73e33e144a08b2acf75cb5ec118","tid":1553652,"uid":171302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:20:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1287987/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1287987/page/1</a><br />\n都可以參考返個結果！"},{"pid":"55a674e063519fda5f598cd09955d8b5d843f3f7","tid":1553652,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a833b5af4f01f92c077edd29c8dd3734c6b8ff","tid":1553652,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55a674e063519fda5f598cd09955d8b5d843f3f7","tid":1553652,"uid":114360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:26:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bc00d7789887b86328a318b34ee895737da0300","tid":1553652,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9dc667b73ee89e487d1cee7727e489da8aae43f","tid":1553652,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"唔好放